<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好啦──！<delay8 />這樣就大功告成了──！！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對了，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你找我有什麼事嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />你在做什麼？</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">沒什麼事</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿嘿，<delay20 />是<tag a="110" b="3" />啊！<delay frames="30" />
你這時候來<delay8 />真是太剛好啦──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="015_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看起來很忙耶</message>
	<message label="015_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次見囉</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想不到<delay8 />我竟然能做出這種東西，<delay20 />
搞不好<delay8 />我其實是個天才喔──！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="016_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />你在做什麼？</message>
	<message label="016_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我沒興趣</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嘿嘿，<delay20 /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說出來你一定會嚇一跳！<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我現在正在製作<delay20 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />健身的時候我腦中突然閃過一道靈感，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果心裡一直放不下，<delay20 />
所以現在就跑來製作啦！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這個<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay frames="30" />
是我的完美傑作，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也想要我<delay8 />教你怎麼做嗎～？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">教教我！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不用，沒關係</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣啊！<delay frames="30" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那就<delay8 />抱歉啦，<delay20 />
因為我還在忙，<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下次再聊吧──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />怎麼反應這麼冷淡？<delay20 />你該不會<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />已經知道<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay20 />
要怎麼製作了吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那當然啊！</message>
	<message label="008_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我知道啊！</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不錯嘛，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真不愧<delay8 />是我的好對手啊。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我本來<delay20 />是這麼打算啦，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過你身上帶著的東西太多了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可惜了，這樣我沒辦法給你耶，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦！<delay20 />我有記下來，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以教你沒問題喔──！</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />就連我都可以輕鬆完成，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你隨便做做也沒問題的啦！！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />加油──！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼簡單就能做出<delay8 />
<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然會想多教一些人怎麼做啊──！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然這樣，<delay8 />我就把方程式交給你，<delay20 />
要是有人不知道，<delay8 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就把方程式交給他吧？<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我姑且有好好寫下來，<delay8 />應該看得懂啦。<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家能做做看的話，<delay8 />
我會很高興喔──！<tag a="110" b="6" /></message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那<delay8 />方程式就交給你啦！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可別弄丟了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />關於製作這個需要用到的南瓜，<delay20 />
我推薦你從種植南瓜苗開始。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還可以順便揮灑汗水喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那個只要有不同顏色的南瓜，<delay8 />
就可以進行改造！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要多種一些南瓜，<delay20 />
到時候就會出現不同顏色的南瓜喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當然，努力和氣勢是必要的——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="032" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦，<delay8 />你來拿<delay20 />我剛剛沒能給你的東西啊？</message>
	<message label="033" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">什麼<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你早就知道了嗎——！？<10_4 />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可惡，被搶先一步了啊！</message>
	<message label="034" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />那這樣好了，反正機會難得，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就分一點我的<colour id="1" />南瓜<colour id="65535" />給你吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有很多，不用跟我客氣——！</message>
	<message label="035" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看你是要拿來當作材料還是拿來種。<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />反正<delay8 />你愛怎麼用<delay20 />
就怎麼用啦——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="036" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我就給你其他好東西吧！<delay40 />
話說萬聖節快到了吧？<delay20 />
說到萬聖節<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒錯，<delay8 />就是<colour id="1" />糖果<colour id="65535" />啦——！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="037" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬聖節開始前需要準備大量<colour id="1" />糖果<colour id="65535" />喔！<delay40 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你就把這也算進去吧——！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
